    "body": "In qtconsole, IPython.utils.encoding.DEFAULT_ENCODING is cp1252 (broken display), in cmd.exe that value is cp850(displays OK).\n\nNote that doing \"a = !ls\" works on both cases -> filenames get returned in a list a BYTES objects, representing filenames in UTF8. \n"
